user.biography: Family of five on a mission to help feed children. For every ethically produced, hand-knit doll sold, we provide 10 meals to children in need.

node.text:
Oh, the places you’ll grow.✨ Noah the dog is proud to have been this joyful little one’s BFF throughout his first year. Happy birthday, Xander!⁠
⁠
Did you know that our hand-knit dolls are the same length of an average newborn? It makes them unbearably adorable milestone markers to track your little one’s growth! That first photo side-by-side makes our hearts melt every time.💙⁠
⁠
Remember to tag #MilestonesForMeals, and we’ll donate 1 meal in you and your little one’s honour.🍲⁠
⁠

Everything’s better in twos.💕 Today we are DOUBLING your impact + giving you 2X rewards + FREE shipping for our Kind Rewards Member Appreciation Event!🎉⁠
⁠
That means every hand-knit doll will give 20 meals instead of 10, and Kind Rewards members can twice the rewards, up to 20% back, on each purchase. Just add your favourite dolls, and your rewards + meals will be automatically applied!⁠

We are ever so grateful for the incredible things our supporters have helped us achieve. Since we started cuddle+kind 5 years ago, you’ve helped us provide over 18 MILLION meals to children in need! We think that’s pretty amazing. ⁠

Tap the link in our bio to shop + make double the impact!✨⁠

Kind little crew.💞 As parents, it’s very important to us that our lovingly handcrafted dolls bring your little one comfort, and also inspire them to spread kindness. ⁠
